title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Sep 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Sep 21 2022
description:
Stocks fall as Fed raises rates as expected and promises more. The latest on the civil case filed against Trump by NY AG Letitia James. Montage of James vowing to get Trump. Democrats now seem almost certain to indict Trump for something. Caller agrees with Buck on the royals. Fauci scolds Biden: The pandemic isn't over. Former Trump WH staffer Brian Morgenstern dishes to C&B on "St. Anthony" Fauci behind closed doors. House of the Dragon and Clay and Buck's favorite party dips.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
